                      2-Step verification is required for all employees and will be required for all students effective
                      <strong>
                       Sept. 24, 2018
                      </strong>
                      . If you’re traveling internationally and need to log into UC Berkeley sites, you can use passcodes as your second step verification method. Find out how
                      <a href="https://calnetweb.berkeley.edu/calnet-2-step/tips-and-best-practices/traveling-2-step" rel="noreferrer">
                       here
